    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a dedicated restoration project or a donor car for parts. The exterior has significant damage, including heavy rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells, as well as several large dents and peeling clear coat. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and will require immediate professional attention; it currently struggles to hold an idle and has a noticeable oil leak. The interior shows heavy wear, with torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and non-functional electronics including the radio and climate control. This car is sold strictly as-is.",
