    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier balance of engineering integrity and aesthetic appeal. Meticulously maintained and presenting a refined profile, it offers a reliable, high-caliber driving experience. Featuring a well-appointed interior and a robust service history, this model stands as a testament to enduring quality. We invite discerning buyers to appreciate the sophisticated presence and consistent performance of this exceptional automobile.",
      "price": 36800.0,
