      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that's still got plenty of life left in it? This car has been such a trusty companion and is still in wonderful shape for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and has been really well-loved, showing just the usual minor character you'd expect from a car that's actually been enjoyed. It\u2019s clean, comfy, and totally ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
