    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a speed-sensitive variable M differential lock. The chassis features a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, maintaining the precise kinematics required for high-lateral G cornering. Recently serviced with a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, this example offers mechanical confidence and a linear power band that pulls hard to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
